A '''Baratheon General''' is a character in the [[Season 5|fifth season]]. He will be played by [[Nigel O'Neill]].<ref>[https://twitter.com/p_iagency/status/531867059467354112]</ref><ref>[http://www.spotlight.com/interactive/cv/1/M119380]</ref>
sections.In the books: In the ''[[A Song of Ice and Fire]]'' novels, the main generals remaining with [[Stannis Baratheon]] after he moves his remaining forces to the Wall are Ser Richard Horpe, Ser Godry Farring, and Ser Justin Massey.  Meanwhile, the small garrison that Stannis left behind at Dragonstone is commanded by Ser Rolland Storm.
